<h2>Bruising or discoloration and Worms in stool</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms bruising or discoloration and worms in stool including Pinworms, Ascaris worms, and Bruise or contusion.</p>
<p>There  are 7 conditions  associated with bruising or discoloration and worms in stool. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
</div>
